{title: Be With Me Lord}
{artist: Sonny James}
{composer: Written by Thomas Chrisholm and L.O. Sanderson}

[C]Be with me [Am]Lord [F]I cannot live [C]without Thee
I dare not try to take one [F]step [G7]alone
[C]I cannot [C7]bear the [F]loads of life un[C]aided
[F]I need Thy [C]strength [G7]to lean myself [C]upon
